            <abstract id="ref1" label="Abstract">A typewritten teleplay for an episode of the television series 
                <emph render="italic">Brooklyn Bridge</emph>, dated 1991. 
                <emph render="italic">Brooklyn Bridge</emph> aired on the CBS network from 1991 to 1993. The series depicted a Jewish family living in Brooklyn during the mid-1950s. The teleplay is for an episode titled, 
                <emph render="italic">When Irish Eyes Are Smiling</emph>. Included with the teleplay is a clipping of an article about the series from the New York Times, dated 1991.</abstract>
